## 5. Route Registration

Add route in the appropriate file under `src/routes/`:

### Route files

| File | Scope |
|------|-------|
| `Index.tsx` | Root route definitions, ties all sub-route files together |
| `PublicRoutes.tsx` | Login, Signup, ForgotPassword, ResetPassword, VerifyEmail |
| `AccountRoutes.tsx` | Brand/account-scoped pages (integrations, settings, profiles, users) |
| `ChannelRoutes.tsx` | Channel management pages |
| `GoogleRoutes.tsx` | Google Ads pages (campaigns, keywords, ad groups, ads, etc.) |
| `TikTokRoutes.tsx` | TikTok Ads pages (campaigns, ad groups, ads, logs) |
| `AmazonRoutes.tsx` | Amazon pages and OAuth callbacks |
| `OAuthRoutes.tsx` | OAuth callback handlers (Google, TikTok, Meta, Amazon) |
| `NotFoundRoutes.tsx` | 404 page |

### Account-scoped (no channel):
```tsx
<Route path="/brands/:accountId/my-page" element={
  <ProtectedRoute>
    <WorkspaceRequiredRoute>
      <AccountRequiredRoute>
        <BrandAccessRoute>
          <Layout><MyNewPage /></Layout>
        </BrandAccessRoute>
      </AccountRequiredRoute>
    </WorkspaceRequiredRoute>
  </ProtectedRoute>
} />
```

### Channel-scoped (Google – needs channelId):
```tsx
<Route path="/brands/:accountId/:channelId/google/campaigns" element={
  <ProtectedRoute>
    <WorkspaceRequiredRoute>
      <AccountRequiredRoute>
        <BrandAccessRoute>
          <GoogleSyncStatusWrapper>
            <Layout><GoogleCampaigns /></Layout>
          </GoogleSyncStatusWrapper>
        </BrandAccessRoute>
      </AccountRequiredRoute>
    </WorkspaceRequiredRoute>
  </ProtectedRoute>
} />
```

### Channel-scoped (TikTok – same pattern, no sync wrapper):
```tsx
<Route path="/brands/:accountId/:channelId/tiktok/campaigns" element={
  <ProtectedRoute>
    <WorkspaceRequiredRoute>
      <AccountRequiredRoute>
        <BrandAccessRoute>
          <Layout><TikTokCampaigns /></Layout>
        </BrandAccessRoute>
      </AccountRequiredRoute>
    </WorkspaceRequiredRoute>
  </ProtectedRoute>
} />
```

### Route wrappers
- `ProtectedRoute` – requires auth
- `WorkspaceRequiredRoute` – requires workspace selection
- `AccountRequiredRoute` – requires account in URL
- `BrandAccessRoute` – requires brand access
- `GoogleSyncStatusWrapper` – for Google Ads pages only (sync status context)
- `Layout` – provides PasswordUpdateBanner, VerifyEmailBanner, main wrapper

