## 6. URL Helpers

Use `src/utils/urlHelpers.ts`:

```ts
import { buildAccountRoute, buildMarketplaceRoute } from "../utils/urlHelpers";

buildAccountRoute(accountId, "integrations");      // /brands/1/integrations
buildMarketplaceRoute(accountId, channelId, "google", "campaigns");  // /brands/1/58/google/campaigns
```

---

## 7. Shared Components & Design System

- **UI components:** `src/components/ui` – Button, Card, Input, Loader, Banner, Dropdown, Menu, BaseModal, Chip, Checkbox, DeleteConfirmationModal, ErrorModal, etc. (see `design_system_rules.mdc` §4 for full list of 41 components)
- **Banner:** `import { Banner } from "../components/ui"` – success, error, warning, info.
- **Icons:** `import { Plus, ChevronDown, Search } from "lucide-react"` — primary icon library.
- **Class merging:** `import { cn } from "../lib/cn"` — use for conditional/merged className props.
- **Design tokens:** See `design_system_rules.mdc` – use `text-forest-f60`, `bg-forest-f40`, `text-h1100`, etc.
- **CSS classes:** Check `src/index.css` for reusable CSS classes (`.btn-primary`, `.table-container`, `.form-label`, `.create-entity-button`, etc.) before writing Tailwind-only variants.
- **Feature components:** `src/components/google/`, `src/components/tiktok/`, `src/components/ai/`, `src/components/filters/`, `src/components/charts/` — check existing feature components before creating new ones.

---

## 8. Create Page Checklist

1. [ ] Create service in `src/services/` if new API (see `data-layer-guide.mdc`)
2. [ ] Add query keys in `src/hooks/queries/queryKeys.ts`
3. [ ] Create query/mutation hooks in `src/hooks/queries/` and `src/hooks/mutations/`
4. [ ] Create page in `src/pages/` (or `src/pages/<feature>/`) – use `../../` for imports from subfolders
5. [ ] Use `Sidebar` + `DashboardHeader` (or `AccountsHeader`) + `marginLeft: sidebarWidth`
6. [ ] Call `setPageTitle` / `resetPageTitle` in `useEffect`
7. [ ] Register route in the correct file: `AccountRoutes.tsx`, `GoogleRoutes.tsx`, `TikTokRoutes.tsx`, etc.
8. [ ] Wrap with appropriate route guards (`ProtectedRoute`, `WorkspaceRequiredRoute`, `AccountRequiredRoute`, `BrandAccessRoute`)
9. [ ] Use `GoogleSyncStatusWrapper` if it's a Google Ads page
10. [ ] Use design tokens (forest-f40, sandstorm-s0, etc.) and reusable CSS classes from `index.css`
11. [ ] Use `lucide-react` for icons, `cn()` for className merging
12. [ ] Add link in Sidebar if needed (edit `src/components/layout/Sidebar.tsx`)

