## 9. Quick Reference

| Need | Use |
|------|-----|
| Auth user | `useAuth()` from `AuthContext` |
| Accounts list | `useAccounts()` from `AccountsContext` |
| Date range | `useDateRange()` from `DateRangeContext` |
| Sidebar width | `useSidebar().sidebarWidth` from `SidebarContext` |
| Google sync status | `useGoogleSyncStatus()` from `GoogleSyncStatusContext` |
| AI assistant state | `useAssistant()` from `AssistantContext` |
| Global state / query client | `GlobalStateContext` (wraps React Query provider) |
| API fetch | Service + `useQuery` from `@tanstack/react-query` |
| Create/Update/Delete | Service + `useMutation` from `@tanstack/react-query` |
| Navigation | `useNavigate()`, `useParams()` from `react-router-dom` |
| Icons | `import { Icon } from 'lucide-react'` (primary icon system) |
| Class merging | `cn()` from `../lib/cn` |
| Design colors | `forest-f40`, `forest-f60`, `sandstorm-s0` |
| Reusable CSS classes | See `index.css` (`.btn-*`, `.table-*`, `.form-label`, etc.) |
